### What's the affected URL?**
https://angular.io/api/router/Route#lazy-loading

### Reproduction Steps**

The hole app is based on routing. Every page is shown via `<router-outlet></router-outlet>`
I had to apply `<router-outlet></router-outlet>` inside the component, that already shown via `<router-outlet></router-outlet>`
I could make it with the only one `<router-outlet></router-outlet>`, but it will cause repetition code and the component will be reloaded each `routerLink` click.

